OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774534302
OL,3,CFans catch a glimpse of what's to come
OL,4,Cin new Harry Potter series trailer
OL,6,FThe highly anticipated trailer for
OL,7,FHBO's new Harry Potter series has been
OL,8,Freleased.
OL,10,FThe HBO reboot is a spin-off series of
OL,11,Fthe original books, with each season
OL,12,Fof the show promising to be a faithful
OL,13,Fadaptation of the books by JK Rowling,
OL,14,Fwho is an executive producer.
OL,16,FThe series will star Dominic
OL,17,FMcLaughlin in the role that made
OL,18,FDaniel Radcliffe a household name.
OL,19,FAlastair Stout will play Ron Weasley,
OL,20,Fjoined by Arabella Stanton as Hermione
OL,21,FGranger.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
