PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774534302
OL,3,CFans catch a glimpse of what's to come
OL,4,Cin new Harry Potter series trailer
OL,6,FThe trailer shows McLaughlin as a
OL,7,Fyoung Harry at home with the Dursleys,
OL,8,Fincluding a shot of his famous
OL,9,Fchildhood bedroom: The cupboard under
OL,10,Fthe stairs.
OL,12,FFans are then shown Harry on the tube
OL,13,Fwith Hogwarts groundskeeper Hagrid,
OL,14,Fand at London's Kings Cross station,
OL,15,Fwhere he catches the Hogwarts Express.
OL,17,FThe two-minute trailer shows viewers
OL,18,Fseveral shots of Hogwarts itself,
OL,19,Fhosting a range of magical teachers
OL,20,Fincluding Professor Dumbledore,
OL,21,FMcGonagall, and Snape.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774534302
OL,3,CFans catch a glimpse of what's to come
OL,4,Cin new Harry Potter series trailer
OL,6,FWe also catch a glimpse of the Great
OL,7,FHall, the Sorting Hat, and even a
OL,8,Fsnippet of wand-maker Ollivander.
OL,10,FFinally, the trailer gives fans the
OL,11,Fchance to see Harry aboard the
OL,12,FHogwarts Express alongside his two
OL,13,Fbest friends.
OL,15,FThe three children were cast in the
OL,16,Fstarring roles after an open casting
OL,17,Fcall saw around 32,000 children
OL,18,Faudition for the lead roles, with the
OL,19,Fteam reviewing up to 1,000 tapes a day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
