PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774534302
OL,3,CFans catch a glimpse of what's to come
OL,4,Cin new Harry Potter series trailer
OL,6,FAlso among the cast will be Nick Frost
OL,7,Fas the friendly groundskeeper Rubeus
OL,8,FHagrid, Paapa Essiedu as Professor
OL,9,FSeverus Snape, and US star John
OL,10,FLithgow as Hogwarts headmaster
OL,11,FProfessor Albus Dumbledore.
OL,13,FOzark actor Janet McTeer will star as
OL,14,FProfessor Minerva McGonagall, and
OL,15,FBritish stage actor Luke Thallon will
OL,16,Fplay the first book's main antagonist,
OL,17,FQuirinus Quirrell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
