PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774534302
OL,3,CFans catch a glimpse of what's to come
OL,4,Cin new Harry Potter series trailer
OL,6,FWelsh comedian and actor Paul
OL,7,FWhitehouse will play the magic-less
OL,8,FHogwarts School of Witchcraft and
OL,9,FWizardry caretaker Argus Filch.
OL,11,FWarwick Davis will return to Hogwarts
OL,12,Fto reprise his film role as Professor
OL,13,FFilius Flitwick.
OL,15,FThe first season of the much-
OL,16,Fanticipated series, based on the first
OL,17,Fbook, Harry Potter and the
OL,18,FPhilosopher's Stone, will be released
OL,19,Fon HBO Max this Christmas, according
OL,20,Fto the trailer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
